spirit:component.spirit:description: The Xilinx LogiCORE DSP48 Macro provides an easy to use interface which abstracts the XtremeDSP Slice configuration and simplifies its dynamic operation by enabling the specification of multiple operations via a set of user defined arithmetic expressions. The operations are enumerated and can be selected by the user via single port on the generated IP.
